Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs30\c&H000000&\1a&H3C&\pos(225.6,546.6)\frz314.6}毕业相册
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我送给瑛太学长的毕业相册
