Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\shad1\3c&H000000&\3a&H3C&\c&HEFF41B&\4c&HDEE116&\frz326.4\pos(456,644.2)}好冷
