Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1B1B1C&\bord0\fs32\pos(785,480.4)\frz9.983}就来初中的后山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1B1B1C&\bord0\fs32\frz9.983\pos(780,518)}有些话想和你讲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1B1B1C&\bord0\fs32\pos(914.4,414)\frz345.8}最后来一次\N一打席的比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H534D4D&\fs30\bord0\pos(423.771,339)\frz346.6}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,听说夏目在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,森川说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那你别逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我还没有赢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有赢过阳斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就比比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天瑛太你拿这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你打个全垒打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,去啊
