Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs40\3c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H1E&\frz29.38\pos(552,397.8)}抱歉 去晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs40\3c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H1E&\frz29.38\pos(552,397.8)}抱歉 去晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都一个月了 还是未读
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fad(50,0)\fs24\pos(502,280)}你那边大学怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fad(50,0)\fs24\pos(445.333,358)}很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fad(50,0)\fs24\pos(423,437)}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fad(50,0)\fs24\pos(619.733,516)}一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H140906&\bord0\pos(566.4,405.8)\frz28.24}看起来确实是那样的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H140906&\bord0\frz29.63\pos(366.4,506.6)}背后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是为了追逐你而跟过来的
